        using the co-latitudes =CE=B8<sub>1</sub> =3D =CF=80/2=E2=88=92=CF=
=86<sub>1</sub> and =CE=B8<sub>2</sub> =3D =CF=80/2=E2=88=92=CF=86<sub>2</s=
ub>,
