            =CE=B4<sub>13</sub> is (angular) distance from start point to t=
hird point<br>
            =CE=B8<sub>13</sub> is (initial) bearing from start point to th=
ird point<br>
            =CE=B8<sub>12</sub> is (initial) bearing from start point to en=
d point<br>
            R is the earth=E2=80=99s radius<br>
            </i>
        </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class=3D"label">JavaScript:</td>
        <td><pre class=3D"code prettyprint&gt;"><span class=3D"kwd">const</=
span><span class=3D"pln"> </span><span class=3D"pun">=CE=B4</span><span cla=
ss=3D"lit">13</span><span class=3D"pln"> </span><span class=3D"pun">=3D</sp=
an><span class=3D"pln"> d13 </span><span class=3D"pun">/</span><span class=
=3D"pln"> R</span><span class=3D"pun">;</span><span class=3D"pln">
