    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class=3D"label align-right">where:</td>
        <td colspan=3D"2">=CF=86 <i>is geodetic latitude</i>, =CF=88 <i>is =
isometric latitude</i>, =CE=BB <i>is longitude</i>, =CE=94=CE=BB<i> is taki=
ng shortest route (&lt;180=C2=B0), </i>R<i> is the earth=E2=80=99s radius</=
i>, ln<i> is natural log</i></td>
    </tr>
