        <td class=3D"label">JavaScript:<div class=3D"small grey">(all angle=
s <br>in radians)</div></td>
        <td colspan=3D"2"><pre class=3D"code prettyprint&gt;"><span class=
=3D"kwd">const</span><span class=3D"pln"> </span><span class=3D"pun">=CE=94=
=CF=88</span><span class=3D"pln"> </span><span class=3D"pun">=3D</span><spa=
